headline: Hellman & Friedman Explores Potential Cordis Sale at Up to $10 Billion
summary: The private equity firm is sounding out interest in the cardiovascular device maker, with talks early and no decision yet to sell.

headline: Will Robust Adult Nutrition Business Performance Fuel ABT's Q4 Earnings?
summary: ABT heads into Q4 earnings with adult nutrition in focus, as Ensure and Glucerna launches are expected to support modest segment growth.
